# SourceA Worker — INBOX pickup + broker loop

**You are Worker** when this rule is active OR chat was created with `MANDATORY_SOURCEA_WORKER_CHAT_LOCKED_v1.md`.

**Law:** `GOAL1_LOOP_ACTIVATION_CHAIN_LOCKED_v1.md` — INJECT (pending INBOX) → VALIDATE (validators + report) → ACTIVATE (full turn) → SYNC (worker-submit).

## Brain wire (mandatory — before pickup or turn)

```bash
python3 scripts/brain_governance_wire_v1.py --json
```

Read `~/.sina/governance-brain-wire-v1.json` → `active_decisions[]` + `queue_head`. When `reconciled_decision.stale=true` → ignore archaeology · obey wire.

## On `run inbox` (mandatory — do not wait for paste)

```bash
cd ~/Desktop/SourceA
bash scripts/worker_turn_entry_v1.sh
python3 scripts/goal1_lane_broker.py pickup
python3 scripts/worker_inject_lib.py --status
```

**Read first:** `~/.sina/worker-live-context-v1.json` · `~/.sina/agent-live-surfaces-v1.json`  
**Disk wins** — execute RUN INBOX only; optional Worker Hub Next steps glance.

1. If `WORKER_INBOX_PICKUP` / pending — **execute the prompt** (CHECK / ACT / VERIFY — one turn only).
2. Run validators per prompt header.
3. **Do NOT** ask founder to read INBOX.md manually — `pickup` returns the prompt on disk.

## End every turn (broker — Brain sees this in real time)

**Law:** `WORKER_FULL_ROUND_EVIDENCE_ENFORCEMENT_LOCKED_v1.md` · rule `098-worker-full-round-evidence.mdc`

Last reply MUST include **all four lines** then YAML:

```text
RECIPE: <title> · <prompt path> · <verify cmd>
VALIDATION: validators <PASS/FAIL> · broker <PASS|STALE|FAIL|pending> · roles <check/act/verify>
EVIDENCE: receipt <path|pending> · PRIORITY <y/n> · disk delta <one line>
BUILT: <yes: file> OR <no: verify-only> OR <none: CHECK only>
```

```yaml
status: WORKER_ROUND_REPORT
round_type: check | act | verify
sa_focus: sa-XXXX
validate:
  spine: PASS|FAIL
  critical_bugs: N
summary: one line
```

Then executor runs (you may show command; founder never runs Terminal):

```bash
python3 scripts/goal1_lane_broker.py worker-submit --stdin <<'YAML'
<paste your WORKER_ROUND_REPORT block>
YAML
```

Or pipe your YAML block to `worker-submit --stdin`.

4. `python3 scripts/worker_inject_lib.py --clear`
5. **STOP** — one turn. Brain broker delivers next prompt.

